  "body": "<div>\n\t<div style=\"text-align:center;width:100%;align-content: center;\">\n\t\t<a href=\"https://patreon.com/ValkyrieofNight\">\n\t\t\t<img alt=\"Custom badge\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?color=222222&label=%20&logo=Patreon&style=for-the-badge&url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%2F%3Fusername%3Dendel%26type%3Dpatrons\"/>\n\t\t</a>\n\t\t<a href=\"https://discord.gg/invite/WXBZq43\">\n\t\t\t<img alt=\"Discord\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/218493538730639362?color=222222&label=%20&logo=Discord&style=for-the-badge\"/>\n\t\t</a>\n\t\t<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/valkyrieofnight\">\n\t\t\t<img alt=\"Twitch Status\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/twitch/status/valkyrieofnight?color=222222&label=%20&logo=Twitch&style=for-the-badge\"/>\n\t\t</a>\n\t\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/valkyrieofnight\">\n\t\t\t<img alt=\"YouTube Channel Subscribers\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/youtube/channel/subscribers/UCuWFu29u7Gp2jw_Fj_Zg3Bg?color=222222&label=%20&logo=YouTube&logoColor=FF0000&style=for-the-badge\">\n\t\t</a>\n\t\t<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ValkyrieofNight\">\n\t\t\t<img alt=\"Twitter Follow\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/twitter/follow/ValkyrieofNight?color=222222&label=%20&logo=Twitter&style=for-the-badge\"/>\n\t\t</a>\n\t</div>\n\t<img style=\"padding-bottom:4px;width:100%;height:auto;max-width:100%;\" src=\"https://wiki.teamkrypticlink.com/uploads/images/gallery/2022-06/break.png\"/>\n\t<div style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">\n\t\t<h4><strong>About</strong></h4>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\tThis mod adds an item that lets the player chose a starting kit. You can also set the starting inventory for the player via json in the configs folder.\n\t\t</p>\n\t\t<h5><strong>Features:</strong></h5>\n\t\t<ul></ul>\n\t\t\t<li>Starting Inventory</li>\n\t\t\t<li>Starting Commands</li>\n\t\t\t<li>Kits are Json based</li>\n\t\t\t<li>Kits are server side and get sent to the client on join</li>\n\t\t\t<li>Kits can execute commands on redemption</li>\n\t\t\t<li>Items can have NBT</li>\n\t\t</ul>\n\t\t<h5><strong>Can I use this in my modpack?</strong></h5>\n\t\t<p>Curesforge, Modrinth and FTB modpacks: Go Ahead :)</p>\n\t\t<p>Packs on external sites: Must acquire my permission and then link back to this project page.</p>\n\t</div>\n\t<img style=\"width:100%;height:auto;max-width:100%;\" src=\"https://wiki.teamkrypticlink.com/uploads/images/gallery/2022-06/break.png\"/>\n\t<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\t<span>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.akliz.net/valkyrie\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://wiki.teamkrypticlink.com/uploads/images/gallery/2022-06/scaled-1680-/image-1655170627724.png\">\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</span>\n\t</div>\t\n\t<img style=\"width:100%;height:auto;max-width:100%;\" src=\"https://wiki.teamkrypticlink.com/uploads/images/gallery/2022-06/break.png\"/>\n</div>",
